  "texts": [
    "Proteinfer has 1100 filters to learn the mapping between protein sequences and functional annotations.",
    "The method was trained on the well-curated portion of Swiss-Prot data.",
    "The finely-tuned ProteInfer maps an amino acid sequence through five residual convolutional layers to create embeddings.",
    "These embeddings are then extracted using a fully connected layer featuring an element-wise sigmoid activation function, which facilitates the prediction of per-label probabilities.",
    "SPROF-GO is a sequence-based alignment-free protein function predictor that embeds protein sequences using a pre-trained protein language model 44."
  ],
